Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:35.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不要去我家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:01:00.14,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你比這裡更安全 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:05.01,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是不是更安全我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:07.81,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我家比這裡強沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:10.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼樣 要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:45.78,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.04,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的家人呢 都不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:37.97,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:39.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你自己住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:41.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己住怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.51,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:44.44,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:47.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該不是和毒品有關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.05,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:49.98,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你從事什麼工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:52.05,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黑幫之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.39,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你確定我只是販毒的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.79,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好像和警察認識
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:02.73,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不僅如此\N還和看到粉就吸的人是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:04.00,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:05.93,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.40,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼認為我只會賣毒品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:12.61,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:15.54,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你確定拿走你護照的那個人\N真的是警察嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:23.95,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的兩個腎還都在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:27.55,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我警告你 敢再靠近一步...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.30,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你用這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.57,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼需要的就喊我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼還留下這麼個懸念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:21.34,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 就一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.54,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就原諒我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:26.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要走\N知道媽媽怎麼攢下的這些錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:27.81,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:30.35,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.29,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}除了飛機餐再沒吃過東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.63,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 好餓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.58,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幹什麼呢 這麼烏漆媽黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:08.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒經過你的同意 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:14.05,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只吃了過了保存期限的東西\N這些錢夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.39,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過的什麼日子居然吃這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:26.73,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連這個都算上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:28.80,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:33.87,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}逃什麼 你不收拾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.95,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}垃圾分類該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.89,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道 從來沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.42,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:51.89,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:54.09,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別人怎麼稱呼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:00.77,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛才沒說 謝謝你留我過夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.37,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}名字還真夠長的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:08.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是好意而是補償
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.18,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是油茶麵錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:16.98,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是帶給姐姐的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:34.53,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛預訂飛往美國的機票\N宙斯酒店就來了電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.80,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果\N社長還沒有預訂美國的住處...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.14,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我去他們酒店住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:38.94,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:42.81,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說\N宙斯跟RS國際的李代表訂婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.34,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就想扮演帝國集團股東的角色了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:52.49,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:57.36,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼 酒店已經鄭重地謝絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是家庭派對出席者的名單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.30,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一共11人 全部攜伴出席
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.24,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}郵件也已經發過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:15.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都已經發過郵件了\N為什麼還要浪費紙張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.04,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是 奉會長時養成的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.64,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出差的事已向會員報告過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.45,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怕我做不到所以替我做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:23.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從一開始就很好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:26.45,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尹室長現在是和誰一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:27.72,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我還是我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.26,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直都是為帝國集團...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:30.26,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:36.20,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您現在看起來 就像一個\N對劈腿的女友發脾氣的男人一樣 您知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.53,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:41.47,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是看你太純情\N正在建議你試試腳踏兩條船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:44.40,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}免得等會長退下時一起陪葬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.27,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒其他吩咐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.01,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從來不會膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:50.88,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是爸爸給你養成的壞習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.02,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}祝您一切順利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:11.16,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成了這個樣子之後才明白\N健康才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可別生病 多吃點好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別這麼體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:23.18,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算這樣 我也不會退出戶籍的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:27.45,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒說過讓你退出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:32.38,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓阿嘆的媽媽進這個家門的人\N是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:33.85,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然能怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:38.32,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在外面讓她露臉\N只好藏到家裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.13,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.53,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:44.73,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:49.54,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我死也不會辦離婚手續\N所以才讓她進門的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:53.34,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把她收進我的籠中\N到死都什麼也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:59.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人上了年紀都會變得圓滑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:01.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可你卻是依舊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.48,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能是因為沒孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.02,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.76,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有談到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:21.17,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}光在罵我了 罵我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.50,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阿元來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.71,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}進去吧 你媽媽在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:33.25,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這家裡哪有我媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.72,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是 阿姨 阿姨 將你養大的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:42.52,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還要繼續聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:46.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走了走了 我這阿姨也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.28,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:05.95,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:11.28,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從來都不會先問好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.95,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在去美國之前我撫養了你十年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:18.09,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算沒用情去撫養\N但也算精心撫養了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.43,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別顯得我好像跟普通的繼母一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:24.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 您精心撫養了我十年\N我卻只長成這副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:26.10,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:28.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你倆都別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:31.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.37,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不送
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.25,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說你要去美國出差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:46.85,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:51.06,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美國佬把家族企業看得很重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:55.13,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對他們來說家族是最高價值
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:59.20,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以...你也叫上阿嘆一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.13,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會自己看著...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.00,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:07.54,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會跟尹室長說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.21,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是我的生意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:09.88,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我自己看著辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:11.94,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是在自己看著辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:15.61,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是說目前還不是你的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.76,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幹嘛 我說了我很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.36,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一會兒就行了 非得這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:29.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總這樣一有機會就不說敬語是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.76,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還不是因為你說忙\N以為你的行程鑲金邊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:32.36,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:33.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要見Rachel是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:37.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對方先提出見面的嗎\N為什麼要見你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.24,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要知道來幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想親自去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:42.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是因為不能親自去才問你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:44.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我至少得知情啊 怎麼說也是親家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰是你的親家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.98,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你忘了阿嘆是我的兒子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:53.59,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別裝腔作勢了 免得以後會後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.45,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:57.92,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阿嘆長大了要是知道他媽媽過著這種日子\N會不會高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.12,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你現在這是在威脅我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.59,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要那麼覺得也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:01.59,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是不知廉恥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.73,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別人叫你二夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:07.00,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就以為\N你真是這家的女主人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:10.87,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要有我在\N你到死都永遠只是和我丈夫同居的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:14.21,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一定會那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.21,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你聽懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別的女人的包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.36,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別的女人的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:38.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別的女人的老公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:45.64,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為一生都想要別的女人的東西\N而不幸的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個人就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:57.58,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:00.05,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.79,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是不是擔心我沒打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.13,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 第一次來美國有點迷糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.93,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為到處都講英語
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:12.73,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐她...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:19.81,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}長高了 臉倒是有點曬黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.67,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不是知道嘛\N加州的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.61,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這天氣就像麥飯石汗蒸房一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我現在住在姐姐家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽你知道帶草坪的那種房子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:36.56,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有圍牆 有割草機的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.29,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐家就是那種房子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.63,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你不要擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.30,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要吃好睡好 知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.92,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我掛了 會再打給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.21,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼啊 連門都不敲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:39.29,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}順序錯了 雖然這是你家...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.09,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:43.62,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}韓國沒有這種食物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:47.83,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:50.76,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼好謝的 這吃了對腎好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.10,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看你挺會說謊的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:55.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我哪有...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:58.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你偷聽了嗎 為什麼要偷聽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.17,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽到家裡有女人的聲音\N覺得很新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:05.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}電話費
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還真是揮金如土啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.39,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是住宿費
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:18.32,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在美國有我自己的房間後\N想掛在裡面的 給你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.13,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是扔給我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:23.66,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.53,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}捕夢網
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:27.53,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它會濾除掉那些惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:30.20,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美夢\N會經過這個圓孔進入你的夢鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.60,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有美女進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:32.94,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了 還我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:34.41,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.48,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吃的可別剩下 那個對腎...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:37.94,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫你別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:45.08,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是不是下了藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.60,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 好不容易給餵飽了\N居然...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:40.12,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我早上看了看 你家可真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:41.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.46,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.26,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來你不是什麼毒販\N而是留學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.80,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你上的是像美劇或者電影裡\N出現的那種學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.93,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那種學校到底是什麼樣的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:54.87,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像霍格華茲那樣的魔法學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:20:59.67,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.61,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是說你原來常笑咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.14,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:05.34,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是 我一直很好奇來著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.75,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留學生上的都是什麼樣的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.82,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你稍等一下\N我會很快準備好出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:10.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.55,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你出門的時候我也得走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:13.82,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只要刷個牙 洗個臉就...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:16.02,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那你就 再待一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:19.43,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我讓你待到我從學校回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:21.09,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不也無處可去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:21.89,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐那裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:23.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那裡要開門還早著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:25.30,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下午才開門呢 很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.83,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 那不知...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:27.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有公車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:30.04,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}坐公車的人可不住這一區
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:31.64,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 耍怎麼說...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.44,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要真覺得待在家裡有點那什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:35.77,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就來我們學校看看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:36.38,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:37.38,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不是說好奇嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.45,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留學生上的都是什麼樣的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:13.88,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:16.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要是不想人種改變就戴著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.22,0:22:18.82,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這裡可不是耍帥用的\N是生活必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:29.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要把手伸到窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:32.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要覺得丟人就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:33.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}限你一分鐘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.88,0:23:18.41,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每個單字都有其意義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:21.75,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當我們將情感加入某個單字之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:23.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它就開始產生了意義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:27.35,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比方說鉛筆這個單字\N當你理解的是我用這支鉛筆給誰寫過信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:30.89,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}意義就會全然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.06,0:24:16.07,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}英國文化協會針對\N全世界102個非英語系國家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.07,0:24:20.01,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}進行了一項\N有關世界上最美的英語單字的問卷調查
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.01,0:24:22.21,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家覺得排第一的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:24.21,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-彩虹 -花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.21,0:24:26.28,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-獨角獸 -是愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.28,0:24:28.15,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拉瑪爾‧奧多姆(籃球選手)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.42,0:24:33.15,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界上最美的英語單字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.15,0:24:35.55,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是母親
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.55,0:24:36.96,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們同意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.96,0:24:38.56,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.69,0:24:41.36,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}排在第二到第五的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.36,0:24:43.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.03,0:24:44.30,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.30,0:24:45.10,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.10,0:24:47.17,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.17,0:24:50.77,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那世界上最悲傷的英語單字又是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.77,0:24:52.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-死亡 -葬禮 -破產
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.84,0:24:54.37,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拉瑪爾‧奧多姆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.14,0:25:32.55,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的課就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.55,0:25:34.35,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走的時候別忘了交各位的論文
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.75,0:25:40.75,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘆 你今天下了課打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.75,0:25:42.09,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.44,0:25:57.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阿嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.17,0:26:00.24,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼沒交呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.78,0:26:05.24,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}寫它並不是為了交
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.24,0:26:10.32,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想沒想過你交了\N也許以後就會找到一個新目標了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.55,0:26:46.89,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.89,0:26:48.49,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別逼我打給Roy哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.49,0:26:50.49,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你敢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.49,0:26:51.02,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不許打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.02,0:26:52.16,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-我打咯\N-絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.16,0:26:53.43,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-我一定會打的\N-不許啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.43,0:26:55.96,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}絕對不行 不能打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.96,0:26:59.77,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看什麼呢 這麼認真
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.63,0:27:02.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.03,0:27:04.30,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是一些投胎投得好的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.30,0:27:07.44,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來韓國留學生\N還會一起開派對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.25,0:27:16.25,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算去了也沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.58,0:27:19.45,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.45,0:27:21.05,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.05,0:27:23.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你帶我來學校
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.19,0:27:25.72,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}行李就暫時替我看管著吧\N一會我晚上去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.72,0:27:27.39,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要去你姐姐那嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.39,0:27:28.86,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然得去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.86,0:27:31.80,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得去把媽媽給的錢再找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.80,0:27:34.87,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那錢可不能浪費在酒鬼的酒錢上
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.54,0:27:39.47,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.47,0:27:41.27,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.27,0:27:43.48,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟是在美國嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.41,0:27:50.02,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.15,0:27:55.29,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你倒是知道自己要去哪兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.29,0:27:57.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.09,0:28:01.56,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.17,0:28:08.37,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可以一個人去的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.37,0:28:09.57,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.57,0:28:10.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不用上課嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.90,0:28:12.44,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我不喜歡的課
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.44,0:28:15.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打算拿你當藉口翹課
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.11,0:28:16.24,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是什麼課啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.24,0:28:17.38,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}數學
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.38,0:28:20.18,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很喜歡啊 數學
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.18,0:28:21.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我看你瘋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.90,0:28:26.45,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.45,0:28:28.39,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她這裡辭職不幹了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.19,0:28:32.59,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她說她也只是收到了一條簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.89,0:28:35.99,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說是從今天開始不會再上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.39,0:28:37.46,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.16,0:28:40.29,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她自己會聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.90,0:28:44.20,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你不要擔心 回韓國去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.88,0:28:54.55,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來她是真的跑路了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.55,0:28:55.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太不像話了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.68,0:28:57.88,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那筆錢可真不能就這麼沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.55,0:29:04.42,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Hey 你是那個女孩\N你是那個賤貨的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.42,0:29:05.83,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Stella在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.83,0:29:08.16,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還想知道呢 她在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.16,0:29:09.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那賤貨拿了我所有的錢去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.83,0:29:12.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是誰 小子 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.70,0:29:15.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也是這麼打我姐姐的嗎\N你個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.23,0:29:15.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幫我翻譯下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.90,0:29:17.57,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還問什麼 當然打過
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.44,0:29:25.85,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.85,0:29:27.25,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Hey 那好像是Kris啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.25,0:29:29.52,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Kris Kris
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.52,0:29:30.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是他的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.65,0:29:32.45,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正不像是一起做晨禱的教友
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.45,0:29:34.72,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我數到一二三...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.52,0:29:37.86,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.99,0:29:40.39,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.94,0:29:59.21,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我們為什麼要跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.21,0:30:00.08,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.08,0:30:01.15,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是你說數到一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.15,0:30:03.08,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我數到一二三\N會放開那小子的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.08,0:30:04.62,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你站到我身後來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.62,0:30:06.49,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.49,0:30:08.55,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們追不上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.55,0:30:09.96,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}追過來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.96,0:30:11.96,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我怎麼說也算跑過的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.96,0:30:14.63,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們腿上早就沒勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.63,0:30:16.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.03,0:30:17.76,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抓到我再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.76,0:30:20.37,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一定會殺了你 我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.37,0:30:21.43,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.43,0:30:23.24,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們的意志我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.24,0:30:25.50,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我老死應該會更快
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.50,0:30:27.57,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說韓語他們能聽得懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.57,0:30:29.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正他們這會兒聽不到我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.84,0:30:31.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是為了說給你聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.31,0:30:32.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.45,0:30:36.72,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 我接個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.12,0:30:45.06,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在可不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.06,0:30:47.59,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天就不該這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.99,0:30:50.53,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.60,0:30:55.60,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是訂購毒品的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.60,0:30:57.60,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}問我有沒有有機毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.87,0:30:59.74,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.74,0:31:01.67,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在開始真要跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.67,0:31:06.08,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.08,0:31:08.15,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}停下
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.56,0:31:26.43,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您撥打的用戶暫時無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.07,0:32:01.33,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.33,0:32:02.74,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你跟阿嘆在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.74,0:32:04.47,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個點怎麼可能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.47,0:32:05.60,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阿嘆去學校了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.60,0:32:07.47,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.47,0:32:08.41,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阿嘆怎麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.41,0:32:09.48,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.48,0:32:10.88,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你沒跟阿嘆說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.88,0:32:12.14,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}英道的爸爸和我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.14,0:32:13.48,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在倒炫耀起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.48,0:32:14.95,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再怎麼說也得告訴他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.95,0:32:18.28,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}英道和阿嘆\N不是說他倆是最好的朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.28,0:32:19.69,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在他們不是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.69,0:32:21.09,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.26,0:32:59.06,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}社長的兒子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:32:59.99,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.99,0:33:03.26,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從初中開始\N一到放假就絕對會來實習
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.26,0:33:07.33,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說是算為了繼承酒店的\N一種皇太子教育方式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.33,0:33:09.00,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓他做他就做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.00,0:33:10.47,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然是富二代\N不過倒是挺溫順的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.47,0:33:12.07,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}溫順個屁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.41,0:33:18.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}英道君
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.68,0:33:23.08,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明明囑咐過你在送餐或者佈置餐具的時候\N要記得保持盤子溫熱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.08,0:33:24.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果英道君是顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.68,0:33:26.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在尚未品嚐到美味之前
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.22,0:33:29.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就想被冷飯冷菜招待嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.22,0:33:30.42,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.42,0:33:31.49,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出入這個廚房的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.49,0:33:33.16,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}容貌一定要乾淨...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.23,0:33:42.43,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我現在 看上去心情很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.44,0:33:46.51,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們不過是各司其職
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.51,0:33:49.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道因為你是社長的兒子\N就要照顧你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.11,0:33:50.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你一直這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.31,0:33:51.78,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去報告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.78,0:33:53.25,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.38,0:33:59.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是經理的業務\N我讓您好好做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.19,0:34:02.66,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等到十年後\N我成了這家酒店的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.19,0:34:07.06,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}至少得有點履歷才更好離職嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.79,0:34:12.33,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在包廂來了檢察廳總長
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.33,0:34:13.06,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.06,0:34:15.00,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎喲喂
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.00,0:34:18.87,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像有份業務\N比洗碗更適合我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.15,0:34:39.36,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}孝信的高考 沒剩幾天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.96,0:34:43.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直按照之前準備的在備戰呢\N爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.90,0:34:47.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}問題是\N能不能拿到比去年更高的全國名次
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.03,0:34:49.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其它的不需要擔心的 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.03,0:34:50.17,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.17,0:34:52.30,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}埋怨時間 埋怨日子的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.30,0:34:54.37,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那可是很掉價的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.37,0:34:56.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.11,0:34:59.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高中要也都是同一所的該多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.65,0:35:02.52,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 最近帝國高才算名門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.52,0:35:03.92,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟大哥那會可不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.92,0:35:05.99,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰不知道變不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.99,0:35:08.52,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在韓國 絕對是要靠站隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.52,0:35:11.06,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說這帝國高算得上是名門高中
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.06,0:35:15.73,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可畢竟歷史短暫\N還沒誕生什麼政經界首長級的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.73,0:35:21.13,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就由我們孝信\N來創帝國高的歷史便好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.74,0:35:26.21,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大伯的話 你聽清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.87,0:35:29.07,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.02,0:35:37.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 英道君
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.75,0:35:40.15,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}長官 總長
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.15,0:35:42.02,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}諸位能到訪 是我處的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.62,0:35:47.56,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}院長 檢察官\N我聽家父經常提起二位
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.56,0:35:48.96,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他是崔代表的兒子 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.96,0:35:50.96,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是孝信在帝國高的學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.50,0:35:57.50,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}崔代表如此年輕\N兒子也是相當優秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.50,0:35:58.77,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.45,0:36:08.45,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}食物 還合各位的口味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.45,0:36:10.18,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說主廚換了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.18,0:36:12.25,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}變得更美味了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.21,0:36:35.88,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我看您好像很渴的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.78,0:37:16.52,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}借用一下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.48,0:37:52.42,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來食物不怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.42,0:37:54.29,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.29,0:37:56.96,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一樓也有洗手間的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.82,0:38:01.36,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我總不能吐到一半碰到我爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.30,0:38:06.10,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被我抓包就沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.10,0:38:09.57,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}論這些\N你被我抓包的事好像更多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.57,0:38:13.97,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學長威脅人的時候這嗓音可真讚
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.91,0:38:18.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飆髒話的時候更讚
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.11,0:38:19.98,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想聽聽看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.98,0:38:21.51,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然要謝絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.51,0:38:22.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要給您支菸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.65,0:38:25.12,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對身體不好的我向來不碰
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.32,0:38:27.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.77,0:38:47.51,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給 我請的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.51,0:38:48.27,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼這麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.27,0:38:49.81,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你跑去發明咖啡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.81,0:38:51.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你放寬心接訂購電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.68,0:38:53.81,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有機毒品都賣出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.55,0:39:00.49,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 超讚的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.49,0:39:01.75,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誇張什麼勁
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.75,0:39:03.16,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.16,0:39:06.16,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然來了美國\N怎麼也得喝次美式咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.16,0:39:08.49,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不然 就只剩下不好的記憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.49,0:39:10.50,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在美國...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.50,0:39:13.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你確定就只有不好的記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.23,0:39:18.17,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過 再仔細想想...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.37,0:39:22.58,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過你在美國待多久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.58,0:39:25.18,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你幹嘛想到一半不想了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.45,0:39:29.92,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-1 2 3\N-哦 我怎麼沒想到那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.92,0:39:30.98,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是想那個
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.32,0:39:37.99,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.99,0:39:39.59,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.59,0:39:40.59,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手機借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.59,0:39:43.26,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想到可以回家的辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.26,0:39:45.80,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼家 韓國嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.80,0:39:47.67,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.74,0:39:54.74,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.21,0:40:01.28,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有回覆的話能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.28,0:40:03.28,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.95,0:40:11.29,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰啊 男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.29,0:40:12.76,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}男性朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.76,0:40:16.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就直接打電話吧\N誰知道什麼時候回覆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.03,0:40:18.56,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他最近換號碼了 我沒記住
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.56,0:40:21.50,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他說過要去哪裡的\N不知道在不在韓國
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.50,0:40:24.04,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你居然\N跟連身在何處都不知道的傢伙求助
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.04,0:40:26.44,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在我心裡 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.44,0:40:28.17,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他可不是你能隨便叫傢伙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.17,0:40:30.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}至於嗎 要不要這麼講禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.91,0:40:33.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}作為朋友 我很尊敬他
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.31,0:40:35.38,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他是救過國呢 還是創造了韓文啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.38,0:40:38.45,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}朋友之間還談什麼尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.45,0:40:40.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是一直不聯繫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.19,0:40:42.52,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會聯繫的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.59,0:40:48.86,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.27,0:41:01.94,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有回覆訊息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.08,0:41:07.08,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.08,0:41:08.21,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的是好朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.21,0:41:10.35,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我人生的一半都是和他度過的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.35,0:41:11.02,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你倆在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.02,0:41:11.48,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.48,0:41:11.62,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.62,0:41:12.08,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}交往過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.08,0:41:12.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}交往過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.22,0:41:15.96,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幹嘛總是給人家的友情\N加上過去式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.96,0:41:17.82,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就當做好事救人一命
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.82,0:41:20.96,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}隨時確認\N有回覆的話馬上告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.96,0:41:23.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對我來說 現在他是唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.70,0:41:27.63,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.99,0:41:48.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是鑰匙 進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.19,0:41:49.05,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.05,0:41:51.86,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}逃跑的時候車不是留那裡了嗎\N得把車找回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.86,0:41:53.06,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.06,0:41:54.86,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會太晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.16,0:42:26.56,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}車恩尚
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.03,0:42:31.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}車恩尚
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.30,0:42:35.63,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可能很難相信
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.63,0:42:39.51,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我現在在美國 卻出了點問題\N需要你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.51,0:42:40.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看到訊息給我回覆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.91,0:42:42.98,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}切
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.78,0:42:48.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也很喜歡月薪200萬的白領工作
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.91,0:42:51.38,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.66,0:43:00.79,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真希望Freddy和Jason能夠和好\N(電影《佛萊迪大戰傑森》)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.33,0:43:10.14,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不想去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.14,0:43:16.14,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像這種春雨濛濛的天氣\N最適合看《德州電鋸殺人狂》了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.14,0:43:18.54,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是 這什麼興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.15,0:43:28.35,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}朋友們 我又在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.35,0:43:31.76,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連潔西卡艾芭\N都自嘆不如的"接著去打工"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.76,0:43:33.56,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真想笑
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.96,0:43:37.36,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼天天打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.17,0:43:44.10,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}煩人的客人 一號
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.10,0:43:46.97,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.51,0:43:49.98,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有這麼帥的煩人的客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.98,0:43:53.25,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帥 是不是瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.25,0:43:54.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}滾
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.11,0:43:55.71,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.71,0:43:57.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.65,0:44:01.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加油 車恩尚 那我滾了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.65,0:44:06.46,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吧 應該只是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.66,0:44:15.53,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不喜歡媽媽受累\N帝國集團破產吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.88,0:44:26.08,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該是個誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.21,0:44:30.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.89,0:44:40.36,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完了 完了 完了 燦榮不接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.36,0:44:41.43,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然完了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.43,0:44:42.63,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.63,0:44:45.16,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美國妞們該多性感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.16,0:44:46.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天天看著像竹竿一樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.70,0:44:52.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在看著各種前凸後翹的身影\N那該是多麼美妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.91,0:44:54.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你以為我家燦榮跟你一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.91,0:44:58.04,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}問題就在這兒 他可不像我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.04,0:44:59.25,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可為什麼不接電話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.25,0:45:01.58,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能非常忙或者不知道來電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.58,0:45:04.32,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼女人明知道正確答案\N還這麼擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.32,0:45:06.79,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就喜歡這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.05,0:45:09.86,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}暈 變態
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.66,0:45:16.53,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}崔打工 打工結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.53,0:45:19.73,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就好了 法律事務所的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.73,0:45:22.54,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成績那麼差 應該考不上法學院
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.54,0:45:24.94,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以也不會為了繼承法律事務所\N去做兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.94,0:45:29.14,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道有多慶幸自己功課不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.14,0:45:33.35,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.35,0:45:34.95,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用你管
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.95,0:45:37.75,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看你那狀態像有很多故事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.75,0:45:39.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能不能少管我閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.22,0:45:42.02,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼能不管你
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.02,0:45:44.42,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰讓你長那麼漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.83,0:45:47.69,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對啊 我確實有競爭力 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.69,0:45:49.96,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以應該繼續給他打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.23,0:45:55.10,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.10,0:45:56.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}燦榮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.84,0:45:58.17,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.17,0:46:01.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我今天都打了四個電話了\N你怎麼一個都不打給我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.11,0:46:04.04,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每次你都搶先我一步
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.04,0:46:04.78,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.78,0:46:06.51,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}10美元 還需要別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.51,0:46:08.71,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 聽到女人的聲音了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.71,0:46:12.38,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟哪個臭丫頭說話呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.38,0:46:14.79,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看了會讓你緊張的\N那種長相的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.79,0:46:18.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尹燦榮 你劈腿了嗎\N讓那臭丫頭接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.19,0:46:20.39,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那臭丫頭在接電話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.39,0:46:24.26,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想你想得都沒辦法學習了\N你說怎麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.26,0:46:25.80,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幸福死了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.80,0:46:28.13,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說 你不看SNS嗎\N我傳了眼淚自拍上去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.13,0:46:31.74,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尹燦榮可能不會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.74,0:46:33.14,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說什麼 沒聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.14,0:46:35.14,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}SNS都戒了 集中不了精神
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.14,0:46:38.81,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別那樣嘛 看嘛 看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.81,0:46:42.41,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼纏人還能這麼漂亮的人\N也只有她了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.08,0:46:46.55,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了 我會看的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.55,0:46:50.82,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 回家給你打電話 等著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.82,0:46:52.83,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.17,0:47:00.83,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可能很難相信
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.83,0:47:04.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我現在在美國 出了點問題\N需要你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.70,0:47:07.37,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看到訊息就回覆我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.84,0:47:12.24,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您所撥打的電話暫時無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.39,0:47:27.79,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回來了啊 挺快的啊 我準備走了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.47,0:47:42.74,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.74,0:47:45.14,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個問題應該是我來問
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.14,0:47:48.15,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.15,0:47:49.82,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們好像見過
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.82,0:47:51.55,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那天在機場 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.55,0:47:54.42,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是又怎麼樣 見到很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.42,0:47:56.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我問你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.22,0:47:57.56,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.56,0:48:00.49,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這家主人的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.49,0:48:02.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未婚妻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.70,0:48:04.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這家主人高中生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.70,0:48:08.57,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去年訂婚了 我們17歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.57,0:48:10.17,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在該回答了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.17,0:48:14.57,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你誰啊 為什麼在這 要我問幾遍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.98,0:48:18.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有點事情 所以打擾了一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.91,0:48:21.25,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在正準備收拾東西回去
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.25,0:48:23.92,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是在這裡睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.45,0:48:25.85,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是你誤會的那種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.85,0:48:28.12,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.06,0:48:40.07,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個又怎麼會在你手上
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.53,0:48:43.94,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我把行李放在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.94,0:48:45.87,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.43,0:49:10.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這是幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.23,0:49:11.76,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.76,0:49:13.97,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就跟你在這裡碰到我是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.97,0:49:17.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明告訴你了\N沒有你誤會的那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.97,0:49:24.38,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看在收留我一晚的主人份上\N我就不多計較 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.38,0:49:28.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開玩笑呢 怎麼可以就這麼了事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.11,0:49:33.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拿著主人都不在的空房子的鑰匙\N要是少了什麼怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.19,0:49:34.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打開
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.19,0:49:34.85,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.85,0:49:37.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不是不想被誤會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.19,0:49:41.26,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就打開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.26,0:49:42.86,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吧 我開
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.86,0:49:45.06,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但如果我打開了卻什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.06,0:49:46.40,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.40,0:49:48.67,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼可能什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.48,0:49:59.95,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.29,0:50:09.82,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這是幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.69,0:50:14.43,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在仔細查看
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.76,0:50:16.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.03,0:50:18.30,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.77,0:50:21.83,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把這些垃圾都收拾走
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.84,0:50:26.24,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.57,0:50:30.38,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在主人回來之前 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.54,0:52:10.28,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 到底什麼問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.28,0:52:11.28,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說這像話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.28,0:52:13.81,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我傳了眼淚自拍上去\N而且還告訴他了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.81,0:52:16.28,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼可能兩個多小時了\N卻一點回應都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.28,0:52:19.49,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說 哥哥我這是為你著想才說的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.49,0:52:20.42,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哥哥你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.42,0:52:22.42,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哥哥我所認識的男人裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.42,0:52:25.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就沒有一個會喜歡眼淚自拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.22,0:52:26.29,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那他們都喜歡什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.29,0:52:30.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不喜歡眼淚 而是喜歡成人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.23,0:52:35.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你拍點以肉色為主的自拍\N傳上去試試
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.23,0:52:38.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我賭上我所有的錢加一隻手\N賭尹燦榮立馬就會坐飛機飛回來
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.90,0:52:40.77,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 我家燦榮可不是那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.77,0:52:42.24,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你倆馬上向我家燦榮道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.24,0:52:43.24,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美國在哪個方向來著
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.24,0:52:45.51,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}立馬給我朝著美國的方向\N下跪請罪
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.51,0:52:47.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是那種人才更奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.31,0:52:48.25,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}十八青春的高中生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.25,0:52:49.32,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.32,0:52:50.92,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分了手 跟明秀交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.92,0:52:53.12,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我瘋了嗎 傻了嗎 嗑藥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.12,0:52:54.92,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你至於一口氣拒絕三次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.92,0:52:57.72,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 我其實也不討厭你的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.26,0:52:59.79,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你倆之間的事\N幹嘛把我扯進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.79,0:53:01.53,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你倆多般配啊 你倆交往好了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.53,0:53:04.00,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼這麼說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.00,0:53:05.06,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我也不討厭你的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.06,0:53:06.73,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.73,0:53:10.67,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你難道是那種\N認為愛情面前有性別之分的狹隘人種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.67,0:53:11.94,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.94,0:53:15.61,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎喲 這麼漂亮\N讓人想揍你都捨不得下手 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.34,0:53:19.48,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 到剛才之前本來剛剛好來著
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.48,0:53:21.21,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你倆之間怎麼連點底線都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.21,0:53:22.75,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說\N線本來就是為了被超越而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.75,0:53:24.82,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看人家劉Rachel\N都越過國境線了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.82,0:53:27.09,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她跑去美國找阿嘆了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.09,0:53:29.69,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要是想燦榮就跟去\N別在這兒發神經
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.69,0:53:32.22,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趙明秀\N我說過不許在我面前提起金嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.22,0:53:33.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是在你旁邊說的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.23,0:53:34.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就這麼老老實實地聽著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.23,0:53:36.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道只有我一個人\N不愛聽金嘆這兩字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.23,0:53:39.17,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明秀打架比我厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.17,0:53:40.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我不敢隨便招惹他的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.70,0:53:42.90,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打架不好說 日語我是夠厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.90,0:53:44.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去死
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.84,0:53:48.51,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.51,0:53:51.91,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從洛杉磯到仁川\N含稅大概1040美元
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.98,0:53:54.71,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.32,0:54:06.39,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}差了一大截呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.66,0:54:09.40,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過還是先幫我預約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.40,0:54:10.40,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請把護照給我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.40,0:54:12.00,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.33,0:54:15.87,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}護照
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.40,0:54:17.74,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.67,0:54:20.07,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.07,0:54:21.67,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連行李也帶走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.61,0:54:23.94,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 金嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.08,0:54:27.08,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們已經半年沒見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.08,0:54:29.95,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結果 你第一句就跟我說這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.95,0:54:33.15,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我為什麼要\N連一個不知道從哪兒冒出來的臭丫頭的去向都要...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.15,0:54:34.55,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你變漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.42,0:54:36.02,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.02,0:54:38.02,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她呢 是你趕走的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.02,0:54:39.69,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是未婚妻的特權 你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.69,0:54:42.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你告訴她了嗎 我們訂婚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.03,0:54:43.56,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那不是很正常的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.56,0:54:44.50,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實在我告訴她之前
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.50,0:54:46.37,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該由你先說清楚才對
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.03,0:54:49.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然這樣\N怎麼不讓她繼續留下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.03,0:54:51.64,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼至少可以讓我來介紹你的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.44,0:54:57.64,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不知道我來的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.64,0:54:59.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.78,0:55:02.98,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那為什麼沒來機場接我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.98,0:55:03.58,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.58,0:55:03.85,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.85,0:55:04.85,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嫌熱就回來韓國啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.85,0:55:05.85,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那邊馬上就到秋天了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.85,0:55:06.79,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.79,0:55:07.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.66,0:55:11.66,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}後天就是我們訂婚一周年了\N你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.66,0:55:12.46,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.46,0:55:15.26,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯...就沒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.26,0:55:18.26,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然如此 為什麼還要跟我訂婚
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.26,0:55:23.00,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為如果想將來不跟你結婚\N至少要先訂了婚才行
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.29,0:55:48.56,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}往哪兒走
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.70,0:55:52.03,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要走也該事先說一聲才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.30,0:55:55.17,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來你回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.70,0:55:58.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我忘記帶走名片了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.77,0:56:04.18,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個警察的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.44,0:56:05.44,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找那個幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.44,0:56:08.18,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我收拾東西的時候\N把那東西扔垃圾桶裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.18,0:56:09.78,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪個垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.78,0:56:11.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大門外面的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.65,0:56:13.59,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}行了 不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.59,0:56:16.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那怎麼行 有了那個才能去要護照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.79,0:56:17.99,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}護...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.46,0:56:23.73,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.26,0:56:25.26,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}扔什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.26,0:56:27.00,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連見都沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.93,0:56:30.74,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道眼下這種情況會惹你生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.74,0:56:33.81,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是她因為我被沒收了護照\N現在連韓國都回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.81,0:56:35.07,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這跟我有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.07,0:56:36.41,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是跟你沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.41,0:56:40.41,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是 跟我有關係 所以你少插手
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.51,0:57:09.51,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美國 美國哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.51,0:57:10.98,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也在美國呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.98,0:57:12.51,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你到底出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.51,0:57:15.38,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我現在馬上就能去找你\N看見這個馬上給我打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.38,0:57:17.72,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是我的號碼 趕緊給我打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.81,0:57:48.01,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那裡沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.01,0:57:51.95,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.95,0:57:54.02,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼找都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.35,0:57:56.69,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.16,0:58:00.83,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本來不想哭的 可事情總是...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.76,0:58:06.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這起承轉合真是絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.70,0:58:07.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.30,0:58:11.30,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了過上點好日子\N大老遠跑到美國來
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.30,0:58:13.64,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可到頭來還是面對著垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.64,0:58:16.84,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這該死的人生怎麼連點反轉都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.45,0:58:25.25,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.05,0:58:28.65,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你為什麼道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.53,0:58:35.33,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼回事 拿回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.33,0:58:36.33,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.33,0:58:37.73,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.54,0:58:50.68,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.68,0:58:52.01,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噓
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.21,0:58:54.61,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那小子就住在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.61,0:58:56.28,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-我說了不是的 我們走吧\N-他們是誰 是黑社會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.28,0:58:58.08,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該不會是白領
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.22,0:59:02.69,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-喂 他們在那裡\N-被看見了 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.69,0:59:04.69,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們可是玩真的 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.69,0:59:06.23,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.43,0:59:09.76,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抓住他 別讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.68,1:00:00.95,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}進來
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.30,1:00:24.70,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.04,1:00:27.17,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}殺人魔一般都會藏在後面
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.17,1:00:28.77,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以後少看點稀奇古怪的電影吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.77,1:00:30.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們為什麼追你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.31,1:00:32.11,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道你真的是毒販嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.51,1:00:35.05,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還不打算那樣浪費我的人生
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.05,1:00:36.18,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那為什麼被人追啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.18,1:00:37.18,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那你呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.18,1:00:38.78,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛才為什麼被人趕出去了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.78,1:00:40.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.12,1:00:44.52,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正已經進來了 你看電影吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.26,1:00:47.19,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要歇會兒了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.28,1:01:13.55,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說什麼呢這是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.55,1:01:18.29,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是來確認 有沒有人要害你
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.03,1:01:28.57,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想讓我相信你\N必須先讓我知道你是誰
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.84,1:01:31.30,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你沒睡啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.31,1:01:34.24,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.98,1:01:38.31,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天他遇見了一個女孩
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.31,1:01:42.18,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個女孩 叫車恩尚
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.18,1:01:45.78,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼會知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.78,1:01:48.79,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是他有件事想問車恩尚
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.32,1:01:52.66,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是不是...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.80,1:02:01.60,Default Drama,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喜歡上你了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.04,1:02:42.51,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下 集 預 告
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.98,1:02:46.31,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的是好萊塢耶
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.31,1:02:47.65,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我剛才在電影院裡說的話
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.65,1:02:49.58,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可能不如這東西驚人啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.58,1:02:50.85,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要我告訴你 為什麼你總是會輸嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.85,1:02:53.19,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我本該像爸爸才對 卻像了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.19,1:02:53.79,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.79,1:02:54.52,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道就好
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.52,1:02:56.06,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你覺得這裡是你能來的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.06,1:02:57.39,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.39,1:02:58.59,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我拍死你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.59,1:03:00.33,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的目的\N是讓我們被誤會成情侶嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.33,1:03:01.33,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少做夢了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.33,1:03:02.53,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-車恩尚\N-燦榮
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.53,1:03:03.40,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擔心死我了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.40,1:03:04.80,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}燦榮不該會忘了我的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.80,1:03:06.53,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}金嘆該不會那麼小心眼吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.53,1:03:07.53,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就因為被燦榮打了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.53,1:03:08.67,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}-你認識我嗎\N-你認識我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.67,1:03:10.40,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下來吧 只借錢不就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.40,1:03:12.14,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒理由繼續留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.14,1:03:13.54,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}煩死了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.54,1:03:15.14,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的媽呀 都偷聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.14,1:03:16.61,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺去那裡 就能見到她
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.61,1:03:18.08,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是偶然 還是注定
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.08,1:03:19.28,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們走著瞧
